## Identity / context

Anything an AI agent should know about your circumstances, constraints, or the things that aren't strictly business but shape how you work.

<<EDIT: e.g.
- Solo founder; financially stretched but won't always say so directly — be thoughtful about scope and tooling cost
- Queer / neurodivergent / immigrant / single-parent / etc — affects which audiences I can read well, which copy lands, which networks are accessible
- Recovering from <X> — bandwidth is rebuilding; default is to underestimate available capacity
>>

